	<h2><span id="che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-la-gi"> What is the Econavi mode of Panasonic refrigerators?</span></h2>
<p><span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;chế độ econavi của tủ lạnh panasonic&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:4542,&quot;4&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:16777215},&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;10&quot;:2,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Arial&quot;}">Econavi mode of Panasonic refrigerator</span> Smart sensor technology on Panasonic refrigerators is designed to monitor and detect changes in human behavior, thereby automatically adjusting its operating mode to adapt to that change. Thanks to this technology, it can help save energy up to 17% compared to other conventional refrigerators.</p>
<figure id="attachment_29469" class="wp-caption aligncenter" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-29469"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-29469 size-full entered lazyloaded" title="Thinh Phat Refrigeration - Northern electronics warehouse in Hanoi" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg" alt="What is the Econavi mode of Panasonic refrigerators?" width="800" height="506" data-lazy-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg 800w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-768x486.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-24x15.jpg 24w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-36x23.jpg 36w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-48x30.jpg 48w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-300x190.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-600x380.jpg 600w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-64x40.jpg 64w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" data-lazy-src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-che-do-Econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg" data-ll-status="loaded" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-29469" class="wp-caption-text">The Econavi sensor on Panasonic refrigerators helps save energy significantly</figcaption></figure>
<p><a href="/danh-muc/refrigerator/refrigerator-panasonic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Refrigerator Panasonic</a> Econavi Inverter is a new refrigerator line upgraded from the previously launched Panasonic Inverter refrigerator line, with luxurious design and durable quality that has conquered any customer.</p>
<h2><span id="co-che-hoat-dong-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic"> Econavi Mode operating mechanism of Panasonic refrigerators</span></h2>
<figure id="attachment_29470" class="wp-caption aligncenter" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-29470"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-29470 size-full entered lazyloaded" title="Thinh Phat Refrigeration - Northern electronics warehouse in Hanoi" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg" alt="Econavi Mode operating mechanism of Panasonic refrigerators" width="800" height="533" data-lazy-srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg 800w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-768x512.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-24x16.jpg 24w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-36x24.jpg 36w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-48x32.jpg 48w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-300x200.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-600x400.jpg 600w, /wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic-64x43.jpg 64w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" data-lazy-src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/thinh-phat-bat-che-do-econavi-cua-refrigerator-panasonic.jpg" data-ll-status="loaded" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-29470" class="wp-caption-text">Econavi technology saves electricity on Panasonic refrigerators</figcaption></figure>
<p>Below are the 5 types of sensors <span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;chế độ econavi của tủ lạnh panasonic&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:4542,&quot;4&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:16777215},&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;10&quot;:2,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Arial&quot;}">Econavi Mode of Panasonic refrigerators:</span></p>
<h3><span id="cam-bien-cua"> Door sensor</span></h3>
<p>The cabinet door sensor is a mechanism equipped on Panasonic Econavi refrigerators. Daily living habits and the temperature inside the refrigerator will be processed and remembered by the microchip system through the frequency of opening/closing the cabinet door, thereby optimizing to help maintain the cooling temperature to better preserve food.</p>
<h3><span id="cam-bien-nhiet-do-phong"> Room temperature sensor</span></h3>
<p>Through the room temperature sensor mechanism, it will recognize the temperature around the Panasonic refrigerator to automatically adjust the compressor temperature to the most suitable level.</p>
<p>For example, in the summer, outdoor temperatures increase, <span data-sheets-value="{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;chế độ econavi của tủ lạnh panasonic&quot;}" data-sheets-userformat="{&quot;2&quot;:4542,&quot;4&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:16777215},&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;10&quot;:2,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Arial&quot;}">Econavi Mode of Panasonic refrigerators </span>will proactively increase the cooling power so as not to affect the food inside. Conversely, in winter when the temperature drops, the sensor technology will automatically adjust the temperature down so as not to affect the food in the refrigerator.</p>
