<h3><span id="tiet-kiem-chi-phi"> Save costs</span></h3>
<p>With smart sensors integrated on Panasonic refrigerators, Econavi technology helps save energy in the most optimal way, thereby minimizing your monthly electricity bill.</p>
<h3><span id="an-toan-suc-khoe"> Health safety</span></h3>
<p>Thanks to modern Econavi technology, it automatically adjusts the temperature in the refrigerator to suit the food, helping the food to be preserved better, thereby helping you use clean, safe food sources, ensuring the health of you and your family members.</p>
